title: Chance The Rapper Gives Away Hundreds Of Tickets To “Incredible” Get Out
text: Jordan Peele's directorial debut Get Out is a great movie, the rare film that manages to work as a comedy and a horror movie and an incisive social commentary. Chance The Rapper thinks so too -- he hosted a screening and Q&A with Peele and the cast earlier this week, and today, he bought … More »
